Basic
=====

Very limited instructions :

1) Connect digital output pins 2 (enable), 3 and 4 (signal) to a DCC booster.
2) Upload dcc_generator.pde to an Arduino.
3) Run dcc_generator.rb, usage instructions will be displayed.


iPhone
======

Very limited instructions :

1) Connect digital output pins 2 (enable), 3 and 4 (signal) to a DCC booster.
2) Upload dcc_generator.pde to an Arduino.
3) Run interface.rb
4) Run the iPhone app either in the simulator or on a real device (having changed the host the app connects to.)